Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:37.31,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死啊！了子特制的玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样！上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝到苦头了吧 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用纯粹而矛盾的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让世界上数不尽的眼帘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法安心的盖上而入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是个天才诗人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己有感而发的诗词意境…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的诗句在半梦半醒之间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在仍在漂荡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊 了子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么鬼 打扮得这么不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想制造一下气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了一个诅咒娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒娃娃？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么还是在做些恶劣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个娃娃不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我哥哥 敏锐的观察力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样弄…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手这样弄…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把脚这样弄…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后这样弄…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！哥哥真有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的把娃娃交出来就饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用刀子指着亲妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲤鱼用自己的身体排成的图形
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个的确就是北斗七星…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不吉利了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强大的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好我做了一个恐怖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直盯着它看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就会想要这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对会如此做的自己感到可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办呢！到底该怎么办！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 就是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托那个人保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人应该靠得住才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人格又高洁 待人又很亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…要我保管这个娃娃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…可是不能够说明原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐交待无论如何你都必须\N寸步不离身地保管这个娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太懂但是我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星当以性命担保来保管这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请转达了子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把娃娃视为她本人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是白天黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用所有的爱来拥抱它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 爱就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远不会后悔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太懂但是我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He defended the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with no more than 500 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes he stood on top of the hill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娃娃已经保管在很安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是了子讲的话我怎么能放心？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 你来念一下 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He defended the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with no more than 500 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes he stood...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我不要紧 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 先做一些伏地挺身来热身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 什么时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更让我挂心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子到底把娃娃放在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点妨碍但也没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了子托我保管的东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时就要看平时的锻炼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在搞什么 真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有一只看不见的手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在操纵我的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道会是诸星…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看 今天面堂更英俊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍白的表情加上一股无力感\N好像增添了一份魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空虚的眼神似乎带着一份恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太潇洒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的母性本能要大爆发了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 让你领教棒球是种格斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打这种魔球吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怨我！眼镜 主角是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要紧了 非常谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被阿当打了安打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是了子的娃娃的功劳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能让一群可爱的女孩为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是它的功劳 了子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 好香啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你发现了 我换洗发精了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当对这些事情还真能观察
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我最关心阿忍的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 阿当真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每次跟阿忍毛手毛脚才会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是吃了什么坏东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错 娃娃在诸星的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子他仍然还不知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被他知道的话早就已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂原来你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁他还没发现时想办法拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的洗发精也换了 好香啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做太危险的事 听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钱有势的人没道理牺牲自我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终太郎 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出 保护达令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话 小事一桩 不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 太危险了 简直无法放松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.32,0:16:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有看到诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟别班的在屋顶上打排球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的家伙 到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星！危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星他没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧！他还健康得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 原来你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂奔的马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 原来你这么关心我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能保护你 我什么也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂奔的牛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然没有发现你深厚的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你一定很难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没死啊 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 在并肩作战中的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝对不会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是个可怕女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然把娃娃交给别人保管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是忘不了玩弄哥哥命运的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像笼子里的小鸟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我关在无情的悦乐之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不应该了 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家剪指甲闭门思过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子小姐 动物还剩下一头…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！狂奔的大象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的挚友终太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友引高中二年四班 诸星当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平日害臊的终太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是表里不一的跟我恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如今你终于解除了心防
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你热情而深刻的友谊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,0:21:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在我的心中 在你我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一朵花羞涩地绽放了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能相信你吗？你的温柔和仁慈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能相信你吗？你的勇气与真心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的终太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跑来救我又拿刀指着我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！我已经忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的把身上的东西交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！根本就是土匪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦 想活命的话就快交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 虽然还搞不太清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你把钱包拿出来？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把藏在身上的稻草娃娃交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一死我也不会交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了子交给我的 很贵重的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么纳命来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说不能交给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只要你告诉我真相的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 为什么不早说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是早点知道真相的话 我就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了第二天…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星 这是你的娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧！很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:22:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 面堂 好危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.55,0:23:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 达令…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整到死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终太郎相亲的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.46,0:23:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是个穿铠甲的神秘少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.95,0:23:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来就是小飞的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.33,0:23:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断掀起阵阵惊涛骇浪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.67,0:24:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相亲地狱 铠甲少女是美女还是怪女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:10.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 我能说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感触是否能传达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:16.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:23.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:36.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的手所拥在怀里 在耳边轻声细语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:50.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远都不要离开我 我会给你个甜美的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:55.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请感受我 请了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:59.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我揽在你的臂弯里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你对我轻轻地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:06.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将日日夜夜爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:12.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人比我更爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:15.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱是如此真诚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:20.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否爱我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:25.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.92,0:24:29.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将银轮偷偷交给你 这是只有你一人的邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:35.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尝试保有它 是我小小的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.35,0:24:40.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定在今日 只有两人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.15,0:24:48.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是公开的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.11,0:24:52.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将准备庆贺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.99,0:24:55.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！宝贝 给你个讯息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.69,0:25:00.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将献上所有的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.68,0:25:04.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.65,0:25:08.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你早些感受我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.57,0:25:11.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来！给我些诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.33,0:25:15.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要我如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.41,0:25:19.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请常来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.03,0:25:22.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将表示我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.20,0:25:26.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我和你在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.84,0:25:30.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如何的美好

